<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,294,1529,1553]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">FIGURE 50.</emphasis>
SEM micrographs of chaetae in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zibrowius" authorityYear="1979" box="[645,902,1530,1553]" class="Polychaeta" family="Serpulidae" genus="Vitreotubus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sabellida" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="digeronimoi">
